{
  "key": 54315,
  "messages": [
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainRoom3_Text_MagmaStoneWillBeMine",
      "en_US": [
        "Charon: Ah you.\n",
        "From the Valley Windworks."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainRoom3_Text_WhatsGoingOnHere",
      "en_US": [
        "Buck: Hey, you! Team Galactic!\n",
        "What’s going on here?!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainRoom3_Text_CharonRedChain",
      "en_US": [
        "Charon: Eh? What’s this, then?\n",
        "Chased me here, have you?\r",
        "I like seeing children try their best,\n",
        "but too bad for you--you’re too late.\r",
        "Do you imagine I climbed this wretched\n",
        "furnace for a pretty rock?\r",
        "The Red Chain requires power. Raw,\n",
        "obscene quantities of it.\r",
        "And this mountain has been hoarding\n",
        "the finest battery in Sinnoh."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainRoom3_Text_CharonUseMagmaStone",
      "en_US": [
        "Charon: Now. Let us wake the thing up."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainRoom3_Text_HeatranAwakens",
      "en_US": [
        "The mountain screamed.\r",
        "Something enormous pulled itself out\n",
        "of the rock face..."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainRoom3_Text_CharonMasterBall",
      "en_US": [
        "Charon: Magnificent.\n",
        "Now hold still.\r",
        "Charon used the Master Ball!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainRoom3_Text_CharonCaughtHeatran",
      "en_US": [
        "Charon: Gotcha.\r",
        "Cyrus said it could not be done.\n",
        "Cyrus says a great many things."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainRoom3_Text_CharonChallenge",
      "en_US": [
        "Charon: Still here?\r",
        "You have that look about you. The one\n",
        "that thinks it can fix this.\r",
        "Very well. Let us be quick about it.\n",
        "I have a schedule to keep."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainRoom3_Text_BuckHealsYou",
      "en_US": [
        "Buck: I can handle these two!\r",
        "Here, take this, quick!\n",
        "Your Pokémon are good as new!\r",
        "Don’t let that old creep leave with it!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainRoom3_Text_CharonDefeated",
      "en_US": [
        "Charon: ...How tiresome."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainRoom3_Text_CharonEscapes",
      "en_US": [
        "Charon: You have won a battle.\n",
        "Do you think that is the same thing?\r",
        "The specimen is in my pocket. It was\n",
        "in my pocket before we battled.\r",
        "Run along and tell someone. Tell the\n",
        "police, if it comforts you.\r",
        "By the time anyone listens, Cyrus will\n",
        "have finished his chain."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainRoom3_Text_BuckAftermath",
      "en_US": [
        "Buck: ...He took it.\r",
        "HEATRAN has been defending this\n",
        "mountain since before both of us\f",
        "were born...\r",
        "And I let some lab rat walk off with\n",
        "the mountain’s heart in his coat."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainRoom3_Text_BuckTeleportOut",
      "en_US": [
        "Buck: I can’t stay in here.\n",
        "Not with it this quiet.\r",
        "Hold onto me, {STRVAR_1 3, 0, 0}.\n",
        "I’ll get us out."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainRoom3_Text_CharonNotWorthIt",
      "en_US": [
        "Charon: One Pokémon?\r",
        "I am not going to waste a battle on\n",
        "that. Come back when you are armed.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainRoom3_Text_HeatranCry",
      "en_US": "Gwogobo gwobobobo!\r"
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainRoom3_Text_HeatranDisappeared",
      "en_US": [
        "HEATRAN disappeared into\n",
        "the volcano..."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainRoom3_Text_Oof",
      "en_US": "Buck: Oof!\r"
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainRoom3_Text_ThatWasWicked",
      "en_US": [
        "Buck: Whoa! Wow!\r",
        "Hehehe! That was wicked!\n",
        "The volcano’s in shock from that!\r",
        "It might be so shocked, it’ll erupt!\n",
        "Nah, that can’t happen!\r",
        "See ya, {STRVAR_1 3, 1, 0}!\n",
        "Say hi to that zippity Trainer buddy!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "StarkMountainRoom3_Text_Dummy19",
      "garbage": 127
    }
  ]
}
